A '''just rigora''' was a type of [[rigora]]. Just rigoras were fought to prove one's guilt or innocence. The loser of such a rigora would have to admit his or her fault or guilt to the [[Pirate King/Legends|Pirate King]].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

